name beamertheme-spectrum
category Package
revision 77770
shortdesc A clean beamer/ltx-talk theme with a big title graphic
longdesc This package provides a clean beamer/ltx-talk theme with a big
longdesc title graphic. The theme is deliberately fairly clean and
longdesc simple in order to not distract too much from the content. The
longdesc one vanity are the big graphics on the title, section, and
longdesc standout slides.
depend beamer
depend pgf
depend tools
